---
title: Hawiian Ham Sammies with Creamy Slaw
description: Aloha! Juicy pineapple salsa, melty swiss cheese and spicy mustard top these little bundles of joy. Don't worry, we didn't forget the veg! A creamy slaw brings a finishing touch of tang and crunch.
